data.description: Seller to give buyer 5k in closing cost credit. Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful 1604 sq ft residence offers a perfect blend of modern elegance and comfortable living. With a roof that is 7 years old and an a/c that is 7 years old with preventive maintenance done regularly you can sleep well knowing that your big ticket items are in great working order.  Situated in a neighborhood that anyone would feel comfortable living in, this property boasts a screened-in pool, providing an oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Step inside to discover a meticulously remodeled interior featuring:? The flooring in this home has been laid out with new Luxury Vinyl Plank and Carpet. Spacious Living Areas: Enjoy ample room for gatherings and everyday living in the generously sized living room, perfect for hosting family and friends.??? Updated Kitchen: The chef’s kitchen is a focal point, showcasing sleek countertops, and plenty of cabinet space for storage.?? Tranquil Bedrooms: Retreat to the cozy bedrooms, each offering a peaceful ambiance for rest and relaxation. Step outside to your private screened-in pool area, where you can soak up the sun, take a refreshing dip in a swimming pool that contains 15,000.00 gallons and a max depth of 9ft or unwind in the shade—all while enjoying the utmost privacy. The backyard has also been laid with New St. Augustine sod. Also if you would like to complete any fencing there is extra paneling that will be left with the home. A stone's throw away from US 19and only 10 minutes away from the beautiful Gulf of Mexico. Veterans Expressway is also not to far away and  that will lead you to wherever you would like. Plenty of shopping centers with major retailers of your choosing. Aggressively priced to sell. Come and show quickly.
